title: Joselyn Hughes
description: Joselyn Hughes is one of Pete's oldest comedy friends from CHICAGO. She is a great standup, improviser and writer from Tosh.0 and she brings the funny, the weird, and some internet clips that make us laugh harder than we've ever laughed. Also, we write two Brian Regan bits and a Seinfeld bit! GET INTO IT WEIRDOS!
